The goal is to balance *contextual plasticity* with *structural robustness*, enabling more interpretable and generalizable models for applications like scientific discovery and clinical reasoning. Open questions include whether to prioritize flexible or rigid hierarchies and how to evaluate both representational quality and structural fidelity.
